OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe morning will begin dry and
OL,6,Fbright or sunny. Cloud will soon build
OL,7,Fnorth with spells of rain, some heavy,
OL,8,Ffollowing before midday. Bright spells
OL,9,Freturn as the rain turns showery later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FBright spells and showers
OL,12,Fduring the evening clear from the late
OL,13,Fevening. Further cloud and outbreaks
OL,14,Fof rain, some heavy, spread north
OL,15,Fafter midnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,18,Foccasionally heavy rain at first in
OL,19,Fthe morning. Bright spells return as
OL,20,Fthe rain turns showery from the late
OL,21,Fmorning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
