OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,6,Fand showers clear north Saturday
OL,7,Fmorning to leave the afternoon and
OL,8,FSunday dry and bright. A band of cloud
OL,9,Fand outbreaks of rain, heavy at times,
OL,10,Fpass eastward Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
